  text: 'A restorative elixir that strengthens magical growth and helps planted crops
    grow faster.


    1. Start the fire under the cauldron.

    2. Add either Pink
    Slime or Blue Slime to the brew.

    3. Add a Star the brew.

    4. Stir the
    mixture carefully.'
